    "description": "In Eldergloom, the Mountain Dragon’s wrath razes cities. As the legendary hero, slay the beast, build your legacy, and survive the wilderness. Craft weapons, face consequences. Will you rise or fade?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/ab49bac319b4d0461a7e133a567af463.poster.avif?t=1747779707\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/ab49bac319b4d0461a7e133a567af463.webm?t=1747779707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/ab49bac319b4d0461a7e133a567af463.mp4?t=1747779707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take Your Sword, Once Again</h2>You are playing as a living-legend to eradicate the darkness once again. The event placed several years after you defeated the demon lord. a legendary dragon has finally awakened and raged the villages around it. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/624a6d685d99bd56f077c8b45eee5ce7.poster.avif?t=1747779707\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/624a6d685d99bd56f077c8b45eee5ce7.webm?t=1747779707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/624a6d685d99bd56f077c8b45eee5ce7.mp4?t=1747779707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>By the dragon awakened, various monsters and dark entities has been increased and cause more damages that no human being has seen before.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Awaken Your Wonder</h2>Rage the enemy with your wonder. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/9f624e1ff4bebf23a0d50e1554a46568.poster.avif?t=1747779707\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/9f624e1ff4bebf23a0d50e1554a46568.webm?t=1747779707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/9f624e1ff4bebf23a0d50e1554a46568.mp4?t=1747779707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose your play-style by combining various type of wonder and skills. More scrolls of wonder can be found in the ancient ruins, dungeons, caves and many more locations.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/eec5b2208a968616d6f091c9dd5a69ed.poster.avif?t=1747779707\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/eec5b2208a968616d6f091c9dd5a69ed.webm?t=1747779707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/eec5b2208a968616d6f091c9dd5a69ed.mp4?t=1747779707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore Various of New Worlds</h2>You will find various unique portals and puzzles which might bring you to unique locations with different ambiance and enemy. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/1cadb471b6587b4e585bf3ac4312f494.poster.avif?t=1747779707\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/1cadb471b6587b4e585bf3ac4312f494.webm?t=1747779707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/1cadb471b6587b4e585bf3ac4312f494.mp4?t=1747779707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Prepare yourself and slay the darkness lays around you<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Craft, Build and Survive</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/a0ccd1a40217fe074c6d0c8467142513.poster.avif?t=1747779707\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/a0ccd1a40217fe074c6d0c8467142513.webm?t=1747779707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034190/extras/a0ccd1a40217fe074c6d0c8467142513.mp4?t=1747779707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Craft your needs for your exploration, upgrade your gear, build your base and stay alive. Make the Eldengloom as part of your legacy.",
